sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Engineering owner
    participant Agent as Autonomous agent
    participant Env as Permitted environment
    participant Human as Human reviewer

    User->>Agent: Bounded goal + constraints
    activate Agent
    Agent->>Agent: Create plan
    loop Until goal or exhaustion
        Agent->>Env: Select and execute action
        Env-->>Agent: Result and side effects
        Agent->>Agent: Verify against goal and safety
        alt Recoverable failure
            Agent->>Agent: Revise plan
        else Unsafe or uncertain
            Agent->>Human: Escalate with evidence
            Human-->>Agent: Guidance or halt
        end
    end
    Agent->>Human: Report evidence + proposed outcome
    deactivate Agent
    Human->>User: Approval or governed acceptance
